        "description_tab": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Product Details",
            "icon": "clipboard",
            "content": "<p>Every great shot you almost got — ruined by glare. Water reflections, car windows, bright skies — your iPhone camera sees all of it, and it shows.</p><p>The MagSafe Polarizing Filter snaps magnetically onto your iPhone in seconds, instantly cutting reflections and glare to give your photos the depth and clarity they deserve. No adapters, no tools — just cleaner, richer photos every time.</p><ul><li><strong>Eliminates glare and reflections</strong> from water, glass, and sky — so your photos show what you actually see, not what the light ruins</li><li><strong>Snaps on and off in seconds</strong> with MagSafe magnetic alignment — no threading, no rings, no wasted time</li><li><strong>Works over your existing MagSafe case</strong> — no need to remove anything, just attach and shoot</li><li><strong>Deepens colors and increases contrast</strong> — blues look bluer, greens look richer, skies get detail back</li><li><strong>Works with the native iPhone camera app</strong> — no setup, no extra apps required</li></ul>"
          }
        },
