            "icon": "truck",
            "content": "<p><strong>Delivery:</strong> 1–3 business days across Lebanon.</p><p><strong>Free shipping</strong> on all orders over $25.</p><p><strong>Returns:</strong> 30-day money-back guarantee. If you're not satisfied, we'll make it right — no questions asked.</p>"
